      1)], "\n    Frame classifier for ARQ frames.\n\n    Input (message port ''in''):\n        PDU
      (meta, u8vector) representing one ARQ frame:\n          byte 0 : SEQ\n          byte
      1 : FLAGS   (bit0 = LAST_FRAME, bit1 = IS_ACK)\n          byte 2 : SRC_ID\n          byte
      3 : DST_ID\n          byte 4.. : payload (zero-padded)\n\n    Outputs:\n        ''ack_out''
      : PDU forwarded if frame is an ACK (IS_ACK = 1)\n        ''msg_out'' : PDU forwarded
      if frame is DATA  (IS_ACK = 0)\n\n    The payload is not modified; the whole
      frame is passed through.\n    ", [''label''])'
